#### `src/index.css` — *Rewritten*

The CSS file was expanded from ~180 lines to ~370 lines and structured as a **design token system + component layer**.

**Structure:**

```
@import (Google Fonts — Inter)
:root { CSS custom properties }       ← design tokens
@layer components {
  .glass-card / .glass-card-hover     ← frosted-glass card surfaces
  .btn-primary / .btn-secondary / .btn-ghost
  .tag-pill / .tag-pill-remove        ← skill tag components
  .skill-match / .skill-missing / .skill-neutral  ← colour-coded chips
  .step-dot / .step-line              ← step indicator
  .score-bar-track / .score-bar-fill  ← animated progress bars
  .data-table / thead / th / td       ← recruiter table
  .form-input / .form-textarea / .form-select / .form-range  ← inputs
  .gradient-text                      ← indigo-violet gradient text
}
html.dark overrides                   ← dark mode surface colours
```

**Key decision — CSS variables over Tailwind utilities for dynamic values.** Colours that need to change between light/dark are defined as `var(--surface-1)` etc., avoiding the need for dual `bg-X dark:bg-Y` classes on every element.

